  "reply": "I can help, but I need to verify your account first. Please share the email on your account (or your full name and ZIP code if you don’t have the email handy) so I can locate your order. Quick note: our system only supports paying a pending order with a single payment method. We can’t split the payment across two cards. If you want, I can help you switch to a single different payment method (e.g., another card, PayPal, or a gift card) for the remaining amount, or we can explore alternatives if you provide the order ID for your pending order.",
  "next_steps": [
    "Provide the email on your account (or name and ZIP code) to authenticate.",
    "Optional: share the pending order ID if you want me to modify its payment method.",
    "Tell me which single payment method you’d like to use for the full remaining balance."
  ]
}

